caption:
@zedd in @whodecideswar for Coachella Weekend 1. 
Guys you know I love a reference! Anton’s album art for Telos was all stained glass. His tour visuals the same. When I came across the @whodecideswar collection I knew it was going to be the perfect stage piece. A subtle nod but a iykyk. This was the craziest set to witness and I’m so grateful to call this work! Big thanks to the team!! Can’t wait to do it again 🫶🏼🙏🏼
